edu.mbhs.madubozhi.touhou.game.bullet

Enum BulletShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BulletShape>
      • edu.mbhs.madubozhi.touhou.game.bullet.BulletShape
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BulletShape>

    public enum BulletShape
extends java.lang.Enum<BulletShape>
    The game will mostly feature a set of standardized bullet types. These have preset dimensions, sprites, hitboxes, and colors.

    Format for bullet sprite names is as follows: [basename]_[color].png

    Author:
    bowenzhi
